{"tid":342080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 欣宜嫁唔嫁得出？","createTime":"2017-07-31T10:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T13:41:07.000Z","uid":41205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc3d61ed7c93008da3ad3a06b98ce2bd0b6e22f","tid":342080,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"當年肥蛆有人射著就有秋官痴埋去，咁欣宜又可以靠咩嫁得出呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nwyman就話報恩比肥蛆寫首女神比佢，咁有冇人會因為報恩去幫欣宜埋單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本討論以婚嫁為前提，話一個人活得自在快樂既麻煩出一出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481180faed55bf238372a29a27fd9543263bb192","tid":342080,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不</span></span>"},{"pid":"751b0cf4c54ec7f5d09720cd676641c33dcdc2b6","tid":342080,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6f36d8e7676147586d6af4b37e15b8bde05cbbc","tid":342080,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"搵鬼佬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a100eef54a66fc897856af4fdc7a7636088d4d0","tid":342080,"uid":41205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Joyce不知幾受外國人歡迎，肥得健康咁好肉地，性格又爽朗。實嫁得出！</blockquote><br />\n但鬼佬男朋友佢都有過幾次，次次都唔得，我有理由相信佢性格都好難頂好有問題<br />\n<br />\n加上其實鬼佬唔係盲，樣靚樣衰可能中西有別，肥瘦係天下皆知"},{"pid":"b1052b782e9b13c3af82f6276bae89811233e709","tid":342080,"uid":7466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"幾億身家洗怕嫁唔出？"},{"pid":"9c78ab58434de0b25af1b4242932d932cd5ed8aa","tid":342080,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾億身家洗怕嫁唔出？</blockquote><br />\n欣宜wor"},{"pid":"66ec3403a387f7b6a07d8440b4ea9a6069b2e117","tid":342080,"uid":60547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如</span>"},{"pid":"1b2577f90a55b63fe8dbfdae15f5ae65fd030318","tid":342080,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span>"},{"pid":"019b3b70627e7922fc5cbd0bcd927866122d78cf","tid":342080,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T22:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Joyce不知幾受外國人歡迎，肥得健康咁好肉地，性格又爽朗。實嫁得出！</blockquote><br />\n但鬼佬男朋友佢都有過幾次，次次都唔得，我有理由相信佢性格都好難頂好有問題<br />\n<br />\n加上其實鬼佬唔係盲，樣靚樣衰可能中西有別，肥瘦係天下皆知</blockquote><br />\n乜撚野叫做肥得健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4a08fa1d4b6eb1dd0ae4b299268fdb833acaa5","tid":342080,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"得閒扑下ok"},{"pid":"9b05761377a5be2ccc11a03252a3aefc3cd89751","tid":342080,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"1月4日報道據香港媒體報道，2008年肥姐沈殿霞離世，外界以為鄭欣宜火速接收母親6千萬遺產。不過事實原來並非如此。記者收到可靠消息，指肥姐臨終前與欣宜達成協議，找律師立下遺囑，規定欣宜要35歲後才可動用遺產，之前她每月只能從基金中提取約2萬元的生活費。肥姐此舉是怕女兒年幼，未識理財，更重要是希望女兒做個有用的人。<br />\n<br />\n痛失母愛的欣宜，坦言幾年間除了面對孤單外，也漸漸學習理財。不過甚有骨氣的她，就算最困難的時候也未想過求助父親。她憶述：&ldquo;試過戶口得番26蚊。<br />\n<br />\n因為工作經常出埠的秋官鄭少秋，與三個女兒聚少離多，難怪看不住個女。近日細女鄭詠恩被拍下平安夜溝兩男，秋官真是好頭痕，猶幸大女欣宜卻非常生性。<br />\n<br />\n入行數年的欣宜，自從簽了蕭定一之後，工作量比以前多了，收入穩定了。早前更首次為王賢志代理的產品拍電視廣告，賺得三十萬，是入行以來最高的酬勞。欣宜說會儲起它用來置業，不會亂花。<br />\n<br />\n外界一直以為欣宜已接收肥姐六千萬遺產，成為小富婆，但事實並非如此。&ldquo;當年肥姐約欣宜同律師見面，在律師見證下，肥姐同欣宜講，若媽咪將來有什麼事，所有遺產要待她三十五歲才可動用。肥姐話驚欣宜後生會亂花，當時眼紅紅囑咐欣宜，話要她做個有用的人，要她工作，不可以懶。欣宜聽到媽咪這樣講，都忍不住一邊喊一邊叫媽咪放心，還話會照顧自己，不會亂使錢。所以欣宜每個月只可以從遺產基金提取二萬塊幫補生活。&rdquo;知情者說。"},{"pid":"0318e2cabf443ddd05680346e1a00a2427ae0375","tid":342080,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得閒扑下ok</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打腸胃係咪有d差，食返清淡d好wor"},{"pid":"3a2b4353374d484d66922f11777aa581089b227c","tid":342080,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔"},{"pid":"79fdba39fb746c1c83daeb0142d736398a27a85d","tid":342080,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"大把人狗衝"},{"pid":"cd806f86e457cf41a50b9d275dfecc51eaf67336","tid":342080,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"鬼仔like"},{"pid":"b8b9714d00f544a4bb00828aa3dc97360ba1dfec","tid":342080,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地</span>"},{"pid":"f36d4bb86c32c273b4da9d11084084c8db9db7bd","tid":342080,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:41:07.000Z","msg":"好想同佢做愛"}]}